    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know, i read about the stomach stuff online but i'm literally in so much pain i can't even sit down. like i'm staying up all night if this doesn't stop. is there really no way to just take a bit more to get through the night? like maybe 1200mg or something? i just need to know if it's actually dangerous or if people do it sometimes when they're desperate.",
